# Force LF line endings in the working tree on all platforms. Biome's
# formatter writes LF; without this, Windows contributors with the default
# `core.autocrlf=true` get CRLF in the working tree and Biome reformats it
# back to LF on every run, producing diff noise that git can't see (because
# the index is LF either way).
* text=auto eol=lf
